title: Legionnaires 33-36 (1996-01) (MaidOfMight-Novus-HD) [NVS-D]
description:
A Novus Release

If you're adding the torrent via magnet link, you can deselect any undesired file in the list of files once the torrent has begun downloading.

========================================================








#33  The Legion of Super-Heroes welcome new members and take on the threat of Starfinger.

#34  The Legion defeat Starfinger, who is revealed to be a brainwashed Jan Arrah. The Legion then learns about the threat of the Sun-Eater, a being that destroys galaxies by eating suns. The Legion are informed that there are five criminals in the universe that have the power to help destroy the Sun-Eater and the Legion needs to gather them for assistance.

#35  While the Legionnaires are off planet, the staff of the Legion headquarters, as well as Lori Morning, battle potential attackers and are able to rebuff them.

#36  The Legionnaires deal with the Fatal Five and the Sun-Eater. Meanwhile, Ambassador Wazzo seems to have snapped after the death of her daughter Apparition and seems intent on destroying the Legion.




Thanks goes to MaidOfMight for this release.
